'''古元古代'''（{{lang-en|Paleoproterozoic}}，符号PP）是[[地质时代|地质时代]]中的一个[[代_(地質學)|代]]，开始于同位素年龄25億年前（Ma），结束于16億年前（Ma）。古元古代期间[[蓝藻|蓝藻]]、[[细菌|细菌]]非常繁盛。

古元古代属于[[前寒武纪|前寒武纪]][[元古宙|元古宙]]，上一个代是[[新太古代|新太古代]]，下一个代是[[中元古代|中元古代]]。古元古代包括了[[成铁纪|成铁纪]]、[[层侵纪|层侵纪]]、[[造山纪|造山纪]]、[[固结纪|固结纪]]。

这一时期，地球上的大陆第一次稳定下来。古生物学证据表明，在大约18亿年前，地球的自转速度相当于20个小时，这意味着每年总共有大约450天。<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Pannella | first1 = Giorgio | year = 1972 | title = Paleontological evidence on the Earth's rotational history since early precambrian | journal = [[Astrophysics_and_Space_Science|Astrophysics and Space Science]] | volume = 16 | issue = 2| page = 212 | doi=10.1007/BF00642735 | bibcode=1972Ap&SS..16..212P| s2cid = 122908383 }}</ref>

==古元古代大气==
[[大氧化事件|大氧化事件]]之前，几乎所有生命体都是[[厌氧生物|厌氧生物]]，[[代谢|代谢]]基于一种不需要氧气的[[呼吸作用|呼吸作用]]。大量自由氧对大多数厌氧生物来说毒性巨大，因此[[大氧化事件|大氧化事件]]来临时，大多数厌氧生物都灭绝了。幸存生物要么有对氧气的氧化作用有一定抵抗力，要么藏进了无氧环境中。大气中游离氧的突然增加和随之而来的厌氧生物灭绝是地球历史上最早、最重要的大规模灭绝事件之一。<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=eo_sMMRxgAUC&q=oxygen+holocaust&pg=PA99|title=Microcosmos: Four Billion Years of Microbial Evolution|last1=Margulis|first1=Lynn|last2=Sagan|first2=Dorion|date=1997-05-29|publisher=University of California Press|isbn=9780520210646|language=en|access-date=2022-05-02|archive-date=2022-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220502062027/https://books.google.com/books?id=eo_sMMRxgAUC&q=oxygen+holocaust&pg=PA99}}</ref>

==真核生物出现==

[[真核生物|真核生物]]大规模涌现应当是在古元古代。<ref name=":0">{{Cite journal|last1=Hedges|first1=S Blair|last2=Chen|first2=Hsiong|last3=Kumar|first3=Sudhir|last4=Wang|first4=Daniel YC|last5=Thompson|first5=Amanda S|last6=Watanabe|first6=Hidemi|date=2001-09-12|title=A genomic timescale for the origin of eukaryotes|journal=BMC Evolutionary Biology|volume=1|pages=4|doi=10.1186/1471-2148-1-4|issn=1471-2148|pmid=11580860|pmc=56995}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite journal|last1=Hedges|first1=S Blair|last2=Blair|first2=Jaime E|last3=Venturi|first3=Maria L|last4=Shoe|first4=Jason L|date=2004-01-28|title=A molecular timescale of eukaryote evolution and the rise of complex multicellular life|journal=BMC Evolutionary Biology|volume=4|pages=2|doi=10.1186/1471-2148-4-2|issn=1471-2148|pmid=15005799|pmc=341452}}</ref>
虽然具体时间点还有争议，<ref>{{Cite journal|last1=Rodríguez-Trelles|first1=Francisco|last2=Tarrío|first2=Rosa|last3=Ayala|first3=Francisco J.|date=2002-06-11|title=A methodological bias toward overestimation of molecular evolutionary time scales|journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the United States of America|volume=99|issue=12|pages=8112–8115|doi=10.1073/pnas.122231299|issn=0027-8424|pmid=12060757|pmc=123029|bibcode=2002PNAS...99.8112R|doi-access=free}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|last1=Stechmann|first1=Alexandra|last2=Cavalier-Smith|first2=Thomas|date=2002-07-05|title=Rooting the eukaryote tree by using a derived gene fusion|journal=Science|volume=297|issue=5578|pages=89–91|doi=10.1126/science.1071196|issn=1095-9203|pmid=12098695|bibcode=2002Sci...297...89S|s2cid=21064445}}</ref>
目前达成的共识是真核生物应出现于古元古代某时。<ref>{{Cite journal|last1=Ayala|first1=Francisco José|last2=Rzhetsky|first2=Andrey|last3=Ayala|first3=Francisco J.|date=1998-01-20|title=Origin of the metazoan phyla: Molecular clocks confirm paleontological estimates|journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the United States of America|volume=95|issue=2|pages=606–611|issn=0027-8424|pmid=9435239|pmc=18467|doi=10.1073/pnas.95.2.606|bibcode=1998PNAS...95..606J|doi-access=free}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|last1=Wang|first1=D Y|last2=Kumar|first2=S|last3=Hedges|first3=S B|date=1999-01-22|title=Divergence time estimates for the early history of animal phyla and the origin of plants, animals and fungi.|journal=Proceedings of the Royal Society B: Biological Sciences|volume=266|issue=1415|pages=163–171|pmc=1689654|pmid=10097391|doi=10.1098/rspb.1999.0617}}</ref>

==地质事件==
这一时期，最早的全球规模陆陆碰撞带形成。与之相关的造山事件有：南美和西非21–20亿年前的跨亚马逊及[[象牙造山运动|象牙造山运动]]；南非~20亿年前的[[林波波带|林波波带]]；19–18亿年前北美洲的[[跨哈德逊造山运动|跨哈德逊造山运动]]、[[彭诺克造山运动|彭诺克造山运动]]、Taltson–Thelon造山运动、[[翁培造山运动|翁培造山运动]]、[[昂加瓦岩浆事件|昂加瓦岩浆事件]]、[[托恩盖特山脉|托恩盖特造山运动]]、格陵兰的[[纳格苏托基德造山运动|纳格苏托基德造山运动]]；19–18亿年前的克拉-卡累利阿、沃里尼亚-中俄罗斯、东欧波罗的的帕切尔玛造山运动及[[瑞芬造山运动|瑞芬造山运动]]；西伯利亚19–18亿年前的[[阿基特坎山脉|阿基特坎造山运动]]；~19.5亿年前的[[孔兹岩|孔兹岩]]带；~18.5亿年前的跨华北造山运动；北美洲南部18-16亿年前[[亚瓦佩造山运动|亚瓦佩造山运动]]及[[马扎察尔造山运动|马扎察尔造山运动]]。

这种碰撞带模式足以支持一个超大陆的生成，即[哥伦比亚大陆]]。<ref name="Zhao1">{{Cite journal |last1=Zhao|first1=Guochun|last2=Cawood|first2=Peter A|last3=Wilde|first3=Simon A|last4=Sun|first4=Min|year=2002|title=Review of global 2.1–1.8 Ga orogens: implications for a pre-Rodinia supercontinent |journal=Earth-Science Reviews |volume=59 |issue=1–4|pages=125–162|doi=10.1016/S0012-8252(02)00073-9|bibcode = 2002ESRv...59..125Z }}</ref><ref name="Zhao2">{{Cite journal |first=Guochun |last=Zhao |author2=Sun, M. |author3=Wilde, Simon A. |author4=Li, S.Z. |year=2004 |title=A Paleo-Mesoproterozoic supercontinent: assembly, growth and breakup |journal=Earth-Science Reviews |volume=67 |issue=1–2 |pages=91–123 |doi=10.1016/j.earscirev.2004.02.003 |bibcode=2004ESRv...67...91Z |url=http://www.gt-crust.ru/jour/article/view/518 |access-date=2022-05-02 |archive-date=2019-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190409162821/https://www.gt-crust.ru/jour/article/view/518 }}</ref>大陆碰撞突然导致大规模的造山，这导致大氧化事件后生物量和碳埋藏增加。据推测，俯冲的碳质沉积物润滑加速了岩层压缩变形的过程，导致了地壳增厚<ref>John Parnell, Connor Brolly: ''Increased biomass and carbon burial 2 billion years ago triggered mountain building.'' [[Nature_Communications|Nature Communications]] Earth & Environment, 2021, [[doi:10.1038/s43247-021-00313-5|doi:10.1038/s43247-021-00313-5]] (Open Access).</ref>

今日瑞典北部的[[长英质|长英质]]火成岩所反映的火山活动造就了[[基律纳斑岩|基律纳斑岩]]和[[阿尔维斯尧尔斑岩|阿尔维斯尧尔斑岩]]。<ref name=Lundqvist_2009>{{cite book |last1=Lundqvist |first1=Thomas|author-link1=Thomas Lundqvist (geologist) |date=2009 |title=Porfyr i Sverige: En geologisk översikt |isbn=978-91-7158-960-6 |language=sv |pages=24–27}}</ref>

巴塔哥尼亚最古老的[[陆下岩石圈地幔|岩石圈地幔]]形成。<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Schilling |first1=Manuel Enrique |last2=Carlson |first2=Richard Walter|last3=Tassara |first3=Andrés|last4=Conceição |first4=Rommulo Viveira|last5=Berotto |first5=Gustavo Walter|last6=Vásquez |first6=Manuel|last7= Muñoz|first7=Daniel |last8=Jalowitzki |first8=Tiago|last9=Gervasoni |first9=Fernanda|last10=Morata |first10=Diego |date=2017 |title=The origin of Patagonia revealed by Re-Os systematics of mantle xenoliths |journal=[[Precambrian_Research|Precambrian Research]] |volume=294 |pages=15–32 |doi= 10.1016/j.precamres.2017.03.008|bibcode=2017PreR..294...15S}}</ref>

